testcase.title: verify response tags in getBiomarkerRecords response

steps.title: I am authenticated user accessing "REST" API
I pass a "query = cancer and queryLanguage = ssql and hits = 20" as parameter to "getBiomarkerUseResultsV3" operation
I get a response with "20" integer values in tag "hits"
I get a response with "0" integer values in tag "offset"
